<h3>Conclusion</h3>

<p>We believe this approach provides the best balance between maintainability, reusability, consistency, implementation effort and long-term scalability while still achieving the objective of eliminating duplicated SQL code.</p>

<p>We fully support adopting Oracle Views for reusable logic and recommend limiting BIRT to presentation responsibilities while keeping common business rules centralized within the database layer.</p>

<p>We would appreciate your feedback on this proposed approach and are happy to discuss further if required.</p>

<p>Thank you.</p>

